The paper discusses the use of Semantic Web technologies in the context of Industrie 4.0, which involves data and service integration, AI techniques, and distributed systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI, followed by cs.SE (software engineering) and cs.DB (databases). The paper also involves data modeling and ontology development, which could fall under cs.IR (information retrieval) and cs.LO (logic in computer science).
